@startuml
title WinM – Общая архитектурная схема

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.2
skinparam ArrowColor #444444
skinparam PackageBorderColor #888888
skinparam PackageFontColor #222222

rectangle "Клиенты\n(Frontend / внешние сервисы)" as Clients

package "WinM монорепозиторий" {

  package "server\n(FastAPI)" as Server {
    [REST API\n(/api/*)] as RestApi
    [Auth / JWT\n(/api/auth/token)] as AuthApi
    [LLM Proxy\n(/api/llm/answer)] as LlmProxy
    [Metrics endpoint\n(/metrics)] as MetricsServer
  }

  package "consumer\n(Worker)" as Consumer {
    [Очередь обработчиков\n(events consumer)] as QueueConsumer
    [Запись в Neo4j\n(graph writer)] as GraphWriter
    [Экспорт событий\n(exports/events.jsonl)] as Exporter
  }

  package "shared" as Shared {
    [События домена\n(EventType,\nbuild_event)] as SharedEvents
  }

  package "llm-service\n(отдельный сервис)" as LlmService {
    [FastAPI сервис\n/ chat endpoint] as LlmHttp
  }
}

node "Neo4j\n(graph DB)" as Neo4j
node "RabbitMQ\n(message broker)" as Rabbit
node "Prometheus\n(metrics storage)" as Prometheus

package "Инфраструктура" {
  [Docker Compose] as DockerCompose
  [Kubernetes + Helm\n(helm/winm)] as Helm
  [ArgoCD\n(argocd/)] as Argo
  [Chaos Mesh\n(chaos/)] as ChaosMesh
}

Clients --> RestApi : HTTP\nJSON / JWT
Clients --> AuthApi : HTTP\nlogin/password

RestApi --> Neo4j : Чтение\nCypher (через драйвер)
RestApi --> Rabbit : Публикация\nсобытий (graph.tasks)
RestApi --> MetricsServer : локальный endpoint
MetricsServer --> Prometheus : scrape /metrics

RestApi --> LlmProxy
LlmProxy --> LlmHttp : HTTP\n(question, role)

QueueConsumer --> Rabbit : Подписка\nна очередь graph.tasks
QueueConsumer --> GraphWriter
GraphWriter --> Neo4j : Запись/обновление\nузлов и связей
QueueConsumer --> Exporter
Exporter --> "events.jsonl" : append\nJSON событий

Server -[hidden]- Consumer
Server -[hidden]- Shared
Consumer -[hidden]- Shared

Server ..> SharedEvents : использует\n(тип события,\nbuild_event)
Consumer ..> SharedEvents : использует\n(тип события,\nbuild_event)

DockerCompose ..> Server : поднимает
DockerCompose ..> Consumer
DockerCompose ..> Neo4j
DockerCompose ..> Rabbit
DockerCompose ..> Prometheus
DockerCompose ..> LlmService

Helm ..> Server : деплой\nв Kubernetes
Helm ..> Consumer
Helm ..> LlmService
Helm ..> Prometheus

Argo ..> Helm : GitOps\nsync
ChaosMesh ..> Server : эксперименты\n(под-килл и др.)
ChaosMesh ..> Consumer

note top of Server
  FastAPI-приложение:
  - чтение из Neo4j
  - публикация событий в RabbitMQ
  - JWT-аутентификация
  - экспорт метрик для Prometheus
end note

note right of Consumer
  Worker:
  - подписка на RabbitMQ
  - запись в граф Neo4j
  - экспорт событий в JSONL
end note

note bottom of Shared
  Общие доменные события:
  - типы EventType
  - фабрика build_event
end note

@enduml

